title: U.S. Supreme Court rebuffs Republicans in electoral map disputes - Reuters
content:
1. U.S. Supreme Court rebuffs Republicans in electoral map disputes  Reuters
  2. Supreme Court denies GOP challenges to congressional maps in North Carolina and Pennsylvania  CNN
  3. Supreme Court Rejects Republican Redistricting Pleas In Pennsylvania, North Carolina  CBS Philly
  4. Supreme Court Allows Court-Imposed Voting Maps in North Carolina and Pennsylvania  The New York Times
  5. Supreme Court won't block new battleground state congressional maps  POLITICO
  6. View Full Coverage on Google News
description: The U.S. Supreme Court on Monday let North Carolina and Pennsylvania use electoral maps approved by state courts to replace ones deemed to have given Republicans unfair advantages, improving Democratic chances of retaining control of the U.S. House of Representatives in November.
